《'''越来越好之村晚'''》（{{lang-en|''Better And Better''}}）是中国大陆爱情片、贺岁喜剧片，汇集众多[[香港|香港]]明星，导演张一白和谢东燊。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.163.com/13/0211/15/8NENTOAP00014JB5.html |title=港星加盟《越来越好之村晚》热点话题爆笑贺岁 |date=2013-02-11 |access-date=2014-04-04 |work=网易 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402142247/http://news.163.com/13/0211/15/8NENTOAP00014JB5.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.hexun.com/2013-02-11/151097123.html |title=《越来越好之村晚》阵容强大 数“星星”数到手软 |access-date=2014-04-04 |date=2013-02-11 |work=和讯 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407080725/http://news.hexun.com/2013-02-11/151097123.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>《新华网》点评其看点就是众多明星给观众拜年的特辑。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2013-02/10/c_124340918.htm|title=《越来越好之村晚》欢喜公映 春节贺岁大片五看点|access-date=2014-04-04|date=2013-02-10|work=新华网|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914100253/http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2013-02/10/c_124340918.htm|archivedate=2016-09-14}}</ref>

==剧情==
该片讲述了新世纪之后的中国大陆农村农民自己举办的一场“村晚”的故事。

